      "source": [
        "## 🚀 TimesFM VN30: OHLC Volatility Estimators Comparison\n",
        "\n",
        "**Testing Overnight Volatility vs Baseline RV_20 for Vietnamese VN30 Stocks**\n",
        "\n",
        "Based on G7 research paper: \"Do extreme range estimators improve realized volatility forecasts?\"\n",
        "\n",
        "**GPU Requirements:** L4 or G4 GPU (24GB or 16GB VRAM recommended)\"\n",
        "\n",
        "**Estimated Time:** 2-3 hours total (1-1.5 hours per feature × 2 features)\n",
        "\n",
        "**Expected Results:** 10-25% improvement with overnight volatility (based on G7 paper findings)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### 📋 Overview\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook implements and tests OHLC-based volatility estimators from the G7 research paper:\n",
        "- **Overnight Volatility** (paper's #1 performer)\n",
        "- **Parkinson Estimator** (paper's #2 performer) \n",
        "- **Garman-Klass Estimator** (paper's #3 performer)\n",
        "- **Baseline RV_20** (current approach)\n",
        "\n",
        "### 🎯 Research Questions\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Does overnight volatility improve RV_20 forecasts for Vietnamese stocks?\n",
        "2. Which OHLC estimator performs best on VN30 data?\n",
        "3. Can we achieve 10-25% improvement as shown in G7 markets?\n",
        "4. Should we build an ensemble model combining multiple estimators?"
      ]
    },
